{"tid":125503,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無發現你既優點同時亦係你既缺點","createTime":"2017-02-18T14:06:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T12:43:15.000Z","uid":67045,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"94aa3e59d884d5c06eb6a4e4cdaa234f84fd652f","tid":125503,"uid":67045,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T14:06:54.000Z","msg":"即係有一種人<br />\n可能你會覺得佢好撚蠢，講極都唔明<br />\n覺得佢成世做波板糖人簡直係戇鳩既人生<br />\n<br />\n可能蠢係佢地既缺點<br />\n但同時又因為蠢，思想比較單純<br />\n所以佢地可能成個人生都好開心<br />\n無憂無慮無壓力<br />\n<br />\n以我自己為例<br />\n記憶力唔錯，本來應該係一個優點<br />\n但係就因為記憶力唔差<br />\n六七年前，邊個幾月幾號借我幾錢<br />\n或者邊個曾經喺背後講我乜野乜野<br />\n或者一秒偷睇前度訊息<br />\n都會記得清清楚楚<br />\n<br />\n就算唔想記得都會記得cry<br />\n連童年時比親戚欺壓既畫面都記得一清二楚<br />\n呢種感覺真係好難受：(<br />\n<br />\n大家有無相同經歷<br />\n你既優點，同時係你最大既缺點"},{"pid":"08970b046e2b616fc40eaa0b58c4b284b4257505","tid":125503,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T14:09:49.000Z","msg":"凡事都有正負面"},{"pid":"ac970156984853d0709f9c60ab99588b3bf84644","tid":125503,"uid":29863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T14:12:57.000Z","msg":"我記無聊野嘅記憶力太好<br />\n好多年前做嘅野都記得<br />\n同fd講番 佢地就話我痴線邊有d咁嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"991027eff951ce2d31b5c67a10464475ead231b9","tid":125503,"uid":67045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T14:14:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我記無聊野嘅記憶力太好<br />\n好多年前做嘅野都記得<br />\n同fd講番 佢地就話我痴線邊有d咁嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明明記憶力好係好事<br />\n但偏偏由細到大  所有唔開心既事都記得好清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf4e7e22f19ab11faf6e65e13f5365556aa5d762","tid":125503,"uid":35193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T14:18:21.000Z","msg":"太好心<br />\n而家變咗爛好人<br />\n遇到啲唔開心嘅事都會以大局為重唔肯表達自己意見"},{"pid":"9ebd9fd8d0e48d8df9ee6f3a4e887f1b6f64a1ee","tid":125503,"uid":65981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T16:30:12.000Z","msg":"記得林語堂講過一句說話<br />\n你最大既優點就係你最大既缺點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cfb8aae26320ca97c87da14c9ef092122906df6","tid":125503,"uid":80598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T16:32:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>記得林語堂講過一句說話<br />\n你最大既優點就係你最大既缺點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nTrue<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾乎所有優點本身亦係缺點，起碼對我嚟講係"},{"pid":"b615993dc69bf1a554aede994a6782b48bcfc3af","tid":125503,"uid":68676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T16:39:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我記無聊野嘅記憶力太好<br />\n好多年前做嘅野都記得<br />\n同fd講番 佢地就話我痴線邊有d咁嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明明記憶力好係好事<br />\n但偏偏由細到大  所有唔開心既事都記得好清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為你個25仔作祟"},{"pid":"55ed5dbb35887f4aac98943c6cf1708eab43b64a","tid":125503,"uid":67045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T11:52:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>太好心<br />\n而家變咗爛好人<br />\n遇到啲唔開心嘅事都會以大局為重唔肯表達自己意見</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我明<br />\n我真係明<br />\n身邊有好多朋友都係爛好人<br />\n經常俾人濫用佢地既善心"},{"pid":"6332896707241baec0e5892ac0eeb0358beab72c","tid":125503,"uid":67045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T11:53:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>記得林語堂講過一句說話<br />\n你最大既優點就係你最大既缺點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nTrue<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾乎所有優點本身亦係缺點，起碼對我嚟講係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但好可惜有啲缺點，就真係缺點<br />\n<br />\n例如遲到-.-......"},{"pid":"c549360015f563ce5eddd4427cc4c99dc3d68901","tid":125503,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T12:10:57.000Z","msg":"記憶力好當然係優點<br />\n但用黎記仇係咪好事就唔知啦<br />\n聰明當然亦都係優點<br />\n但用黎做壞事的話 咁仲算唔算係優點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個人認為你的能力係你的優點<br />\n只係你將你的能力用係d唔好的事到<br />\n所以會變成缺點"},{"pid":"930c2a35a8cbf09c5fca2baf54b912c2ac268f81","tid":125503,"uid":39402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T12:39:15.000Z","msg":"理性"},{"pid":"46a8eaed3f6bf70aba200f809fc0c83024df57ad","tid":125503,"uid":80598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T12:43:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>理性</blockquote><br />\n比人話過太理性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話太冇人情味，冇人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}